Package org.jmisb.api.klv.st1108.st1108_2 Description

ST 1108.2: Motion Imagery Interpretability and Quality Metadata.

This document defines metadata keys necessary to express motion imagery interpretability and quality (IQ).

In addition it allows associated image chips or quality related features to be sent in an MPEG-2 transport stream to support reduced bandwidth, partial-reference techniques for IQ estimation at the receiver.
